          "user_photo_count": 11,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL1uMT3dbVgf67Vfq4T_6bDMUlPTU2Jg--k4EVWX1hVaCRsAQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "The most ridiculous experience. A big 2-level pharmacy. The item I needed was in the lower floor locked iOS in the shelf. I pressed the button. Nobody ever showed up until 7 minutes later I raised hell and someone came from the other level\n\nI went upstairs to pay. ONE register open and a long line",
