          "description": "Would definitely recommend to a friend for a passport photo. I was in and out and the employees at the 53rd and 3rd location in Manhattan were swift and helpful!",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kxTFQzbEpXRFpDYjBWdlpGQnFRV3RoWVZBMlJIYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x31a0fca4a22778d9!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOi1LT3lJWDZCb0VvZFBqQWthYVA2RHc%7C%7C?hl=en",
