          "description": "This Walgreens is just the Worst. The Staff is Extremely Unfriendly and Do not Provide Any Customer Service.  I am in a Wheelchair,  I asked for Some Assistance and the Female Staff Member just stated I'm going on my Break. Then I Noticed the Refrigerator Door was not Closing Properly and I let the other Staff Member Know. And She just Shrugged her Shoulders. This is the Refrigerator with the Dairy Products in it. Real uncaring Staff in this Store !!\nHorrible!!!!!!!!",
